title: THE Steve Wilkos Show 04.21.08
description:
STEVE CLEANS HOUSE:

What a mess! Jennifer is married to John and they lost their two children because of the conditions they were being raised in! When social services came to their house they had pets going in and out of the house and both children had head lice. Jennifer and John were forced to give up their children, and they gave them to John&#039;s sister, Faith. John also had a child with Elizabeth, and she wants him to sign over custody for their child.
